  "2026-06-19T05:22:11.351Z",claude-code-agent,"Implemented pm list --format csv|table (GH-154 remainder). New shared renderer src/core/output/tabular.ts (renderRowsAsCsv RFC-4180-compliant + renderRowsAsTable fixed-width). --format also accepts json|toon (reuses resolveReadCommandOutputFormat override). Columns follow the active projection (--fields/--brief/--compact). Rejects --format+--stream. CLI-only (not on MCP, agents use --json). Tests: tests/unit/core/output/tabular.spec.ts + register-list-query.spec.ts. Docs: COMMANDS.md 'Output render formats'."
close_reason: "Shipped pm list --format csv|table (+ json|toon override) via shared src/core/output/tabular.ts renderer. 100% coverage, docs + contracts updated."
